<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-5"><a href="#Explicitly_hiding.2Fshowing_the_soft_input_method"><span class="tocnumber">1.3.1</span> <span class="toctext">Explicitly hiding/showing the soft input method</span></a></li>
